It was all shades of lit at the ‘Castlelite unlocks’ which held yesterday at the Eko Hotel and Suites, Lagos. The rap god J.Cole gave the audience a night to remember. Nigerians, in turn, surprised him when they rapped along to his new album which is less than a week, KOD. Davido, Wizkid, M.I, Tiwa Savage and Ycee were also there to thrill the audience. In case you missed it, watch snippets of the event below: